com.interpss.dc.pv.module

Interface PVModelIVFunction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractPVModelIVFunction, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IPVModelIVFunction, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVModelIVFunctionImpl

    public interface PVModelIVFunction
extends AbstractPVModelIVFunction
    A representation of the model object 'IV Function'. A PVModuleIVFunction implementation.

    The following features are supported:

    • Voc
    • Vmaxp
    • Sign
    • A
    • B
    • C
    • D
    • E
    • F
    See Also:
    PVModulePackage.getPVModelIVFunction()
